{"to":["emily@innovatenow.com"],"subject":"Re: Request for Background Materials on Our Potential Collaboration","body":"Hi Emily,

Thanks for following up.

I’m happy to share a high-level overview of the objectives guiding our initial thinking so you have the context you need for your proposal:

• Customer value first: We’re interested in solutions that demonstrably improve our clients’ experience and create measurable ROI within 6-12 months.
• Joint go-to-market potential: Opportunities where both companies can leverage existing sales channels to reach new segments are a priority.
• Complementary technology fit: We’re exploring partnerships that enhance our data-driven decision-making capabilities and accelerate product development timelines.
• Geographic growth: International expansion is on our 2025 roadmap, so we’re keen to discuss collaborations that help both firms scale beyond current core markets.

These points should give you a sense of where we’re headed without getting into proprietary detail. If you need anything more specific, let’s set up a call so we can talk through it live and determine what non-confidential information we can exchange at this stage.

Feel free to send across any preliminary ideas or questions, and I’ll make sure the right members of our team are looped in.

Best regards,
John
